        "subject": "LU-5541 test: add proper libtool setup for test application",
        "message": "LU-5541 test: add proper libtool setup for test application\n\nThe work to move to libtools has exposed a build issue for deb\nbased systems. I suspect it is due to the Makefile.am not\ndefining xxx_SOURCES and xxx_DEPENDENCIES which is causes this\nbuild problem.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\n\nChange-Id: I531afb2f4690bd5f72dd1abd974dbf3e6af54659\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@yahoo.com>\n"
      },
